{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectmanagerclient\/onnotifyname(flags:handler:)"]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"extendedModule":"GIO","title":"onNotifyName(flags:handler:)","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyName"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ConnectFlags"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO26DBusObjectManagerClientRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"DBusObjectManagerClientRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","text":"ParamSpecRef"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:3GIO31DBusObjectManagerClientProtocolPAAE12onNotifyName5flags7handlerSi04GLibC012ConnectFlagsV_yAA0bcdE3RefV_AG09ParamSpecO0VtctF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO23DBusObjectManagerClientC","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"g_object_set()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", et al.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClient\/onNotifyName(flags:handler:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClient","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClient\/DBusObjectManagerClientProtocol-Implementations"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@discardableResult"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"onNotifyName","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"text":" = ConnectFlags(0), ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"DBusObjectManagerClientRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO26DBusObjectManagerClientRefV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Flags"}]}],"name":"flags"},{"name":"handler","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The signal handler to call","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Run the given callback whenever the "},{"code":"notifyName","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" signal is emitted","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"code":"g_object_notify()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"text":" call, like this:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"C","type":"codeListing","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is important to note that you must use","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"detail strings for the notify signal.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","name":"Note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This represents the underlying "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify::name"},{"text":" signal","type":"text"}]}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/DBusObjectManagerServer":{"title":"DBusObjectManagerServer","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectmanagerserver","abstract":[{"code":"GDBusObjectManagerServer","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is used to export [iface"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObject","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"] instances"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"using the standardized"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"http:\/\/dbus.freedesktop.org\/doc\/dbus-specification.html#standard-interfaces-objectmanager"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"interface. For example, remote D-Bus clients can get all objects","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and properties in a single call. Additionally, any change in the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object hierarchy is broadcast using signals. This means that D-Bus"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"clients can keep caches up to date by only listening to D-Bus"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"signals."}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"DBusObjectManagerServer","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerServer","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"DBusObjectManagerServer","kind":"identifier"}]},"#class@GObject.ParamS